  "text": "Such switchable systems might find application in the telecommunications field as a variable optical attenuator (VOA) [CITATION_1] . Switching of signal transmission intensity in the NIR region (800-2000 nm) is useful in signal modulation for silica fibre-optics as they are most transparent in the NIR region [53] .",
